data.description:
Nestled in the heart of the scenic Hill Country, this magnificent 5.6-acre property offers the perfect blend of spacious living, serene natural beauty, and endless possibilities. With a generous 2400 square feet on both the second floor home and lower level garage, this home is a true gem for those seeking room to roam and explore.
Parking and carport are elevated on the hillside for you to enter this charming home on the 2nd floor without climbing stairs and the ability to enjoy the expansive views. This area opens to a warm and inviting interior of living space with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home provides ample space for your family to relax and unwind.The living room, dining room, and kitchen flow seamlessly together, creating an expansive open area ideal for family gatherings and entertaining. The extra-large laundry room and doubles as a walk-in pantry add a touch of convenience to your daily life. Step outside onto the large wrap-around deck, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or host gatherings while taking in the grand views of the stunning Canyon Lake area and the picturesque Hill Country. Take the interior stairs down to the lower level, which features an additional 2400 square feet of space, perfect for a garage or workshop to pursue your hobbies and projects.Whether you're a nature enthusiast or simply seeking a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of city life, this property offers the ideal canvas for your dreams.
Don't miss this opportunity to make this spacious and inviting Hill Country retreat your own. Schedule a viewing and experience the beauty and serenity of Canyon Lake living for yourself!
